{"id": "ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 328, "displayName": {"text": "mandarin coffee stand", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkTWFuZDNMWE0xYUdnMVpqQkllREZWZW0xdlNXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "It’s a hot day, a Sicilian coffee is the perfect pick! Refreshing, smooth, and just the right balance of coffee and citrus.\nLight, vibrant, and super satisfying in warm weather—definitely a go-to drink to cool down while still getting that coffee fix! ☕🍋 Only downside? The line can get pretty long… but honestly, still worth the wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It’s a hot day, a Sicilian coffee is the perfect pick! Refreshing, smooth, and just the right balance of coffee and citrus.\nLight, vibrant, and super satisfying in warm weather—definitely a go-to drink to cool down while still getting that coffee fix! ☕🍋 Only downside? The line can get pretty long… but honestly, still worth the wait.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shinyin Wu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109835756565263768620/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZiLBoJZVCLEyc_RJtA_VWehtwG2BPM4ttLlXDc93GrFqyC7wpdg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T20:40:53.343338478Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkTWFuZDNMWE0xYUdnMVpqQkllREZWZW0xdlNXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkTWFuZDNMWE0xYUdnMVpqQkllREZWZW0xdlNXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c349e8db7e21:0xc37b1cf5e9df7b60"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkSGVIazRjMDF6Tm5WeVh6RlNORlZJVmtoTFNYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The Burlington Arcade is so gorgeous and mandarin coffee stand fits right in! While the storefront only allows 4 customers at a time, waiting outside doesn’t feel bothersome because you’re in such a beautiful space.\n\nWhile they do have citrusy flavors on their menu, much of their focus is on serving Chinese coffee among classics. I got the gui hua latte (which only comes hot) and it really grew on me, with the complex flavor combination of coffee, slight spice, and florality. Their Vienna latte was smooth and rich while their honey yuzu fizz was bright and refreshing. There are a couple of tables in the walkway, but I wouldn’t count on doing work here or staying for a long period of time. Parking is pretty easy in the lot, though!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The Burlington Arcade is so gorgeous and mandarin coffee stand fits right in! While the storefront only allows 4 customers at a time, waiting outside doesn’t feel bothersome because you’re in such a beautiful space.\n\nWhile they do have citrusy flavors on their menu, much of their focus is on serving Chinese coffee among classics. I got the gui hua latte (which only comes hot) and it really grew on me, with the complex flavor combination of coffee, slight spice, and florality. Their Vienna latte was smooth and rich while their honey yuzu fizz was bright and refreshing. There are a couple of tables in the walkway, but I wouldn’t count on doing work here or staying for a long period of time. Parking is pretty easy in the lot, though!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anna", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108989905571960919053/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDfJK7w1fmx_Jh1hFg8FS9KuGK4aPUfuyOQ1BU3RzqrmAzH5Y=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-20T18:50:19.533715208Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkSGVIazRjMDF6Tm5WeVh6RlNORlZJVmtoTFNYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkSGVIazRjMDF6Tm5WeVh6RlNORlZJVmtoTFNYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c349e8db7e21:0xc37b1cf5e9df7b60"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd2NUWk1aMFZaTW5GT2FWaHZkME5FZFVWMVZVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Had a really disappointing visit to mandarin coffee stand recently. I ordered an iced hojicha latte just to be told they had run out of ice. Which is really abnormal for a coffee stand. Especially given it was a Tuesday and had very little traffic it seemed. Still charged full price for a 3/4th lukewarm cup of chocolate milk. Quality was horrible in comparison to other places I've tried. Definitely will not be coming back or recommending to other people in the near future. If hojicha latte isn't your specialty then maybe don't include in on the menu. Had to run down to smoking tiger coffee lab for a better latte.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a really disappointing visit to mandarin coffee stand recently. I ordered an iced hojicha latte just to be told they had run out of ice. Which is really abnormal for a coffee stand. Especially given it was a Tuesday and had very little traffic it seemed. Still charged full price for a 3/4th lukewarm cup of chocolate milk. Quality was horrible in comparison to other places I've tried. Definitely will not be coming back or recommending to other people in the near future. If hojicha latte isn't your specialty then maybe don't include in on the menu. Had to run down to smoking tiger coffee lab for a better latte.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kimberly Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103998793636711979067/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbDHaZCCNuSMGcIIA3zOv2MsFaDi0gdmkdzXtsfnkRDTSDQw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T22:00:13.473478101Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd2NUWk1aMFZaTW5GT2FWaHZkME5FZFVWMVZVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd2NUWk1aMFZaTW5GT2FWaHZkME5FZFVWMVZVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c349e8db7e21:0xc37b1cf5e9df7b60"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwR2FtMTVVRWxWYkU1Q1pqQXpkM2h1Y21sNFNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "i am not in too often but whenever i am mandarin is a must. i was lucky enough to be working in pasadena for a couple days and had a drip coffee and a  iced oat matcha one day and americano and hot oat chai the next\neverything was on point. the consistency here is impressive, ive been coming since they opened and i can’t recall ever being disappointed.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "i am not in too often but whenever i am mandarin is a must. i was lucky enough to be working in pasadena for a couple days and had a drip coffee and a  iced oat matcha one day and americano and hot oat chai the next\neverything was on point. the consistency here is impressive, ive been coming since they opened and i can’t recall ever being disappointed.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "hailey maier", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104059600880925751868/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9My1Po8MHW_LP7D1vfeY-fs0eYBAYKjbjnJPyDZ2-RdtBr8M=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-10T01:50:55.342188324Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwR2FtMTVVRWxWYkU1Q1pqQXpkM2h1Y21sNFNGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwR2FtMTVVRWxWYkU1Q1pqQXpkM2h1Y21sNFNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c349e8db7e21:0xc37b1cf5e9df7b60"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21rd1ZtTmZRelF5UjBVM05FZzNRVmxOYmpCUlNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I was looking for a cute coffee shop to go to with my husband and this definitely met my expectations. We felt transported to another country immediately because of the aesthetics they have curated here. We had to wait about 35-45 minutes for the coffee and the baristas were nice. I got a ham and cheese croissant (I would rate it a 7/10) and the Vienna with oatmilk (which was the best out of the Toasty and Matcha) in my opinion (8.5/10). My husband got a croffin and the Toasty, and he liked the croffin more than the Toasty. The croffin was really good, and I agreed that the Toasty didn’t blow me away. We ordered Matcha for my sister to go and she said initially it was average, but as you stirred it up it got better. Overall this was a really cute coffee shop with good pastries, nice baristas, and good coffee. If you’re open to wait for the line, I would definitely make my way down to mandarin to try out their coffee!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I was looking for a cute coffee shop to go to with my husband and this definitely met my expectations. We felt transported to another country immediately because of the aesthetics they have curated here. We had to wait about 35-45 minutes for the coffee and the baristas were nice. I got a ham and cheese croissant (I would rate it a 7/10) and the Vienna with oatmilk (which was the best out of the Toasty and Matcha) in my opinion (8.5/10). My husband got a croffin and the Toasty, and he liked the croffin more than the Toasty. The croffin was really good, and I agreed that the Toasty didn’t blow me away. We ordered Matcha for my sister to go and she said initially it was average, but as you stirred it up it got better. Overall this was a really cute coffee shop with good pastries, nice baristas, and good coffee. If you’re open to wait for the line, I would definitely make my way down to mandarin to try out their coffee!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brittany Mendez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101437992643882599974/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_dmOYtM2iR5YV9cmogPof5xyrT4bqJVel6sfp3OKp5W4lMLyYHw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-12T18:06:13.060690499Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21rd1ZtTmZRelF5UjBVM05FZzNRVmxOYmpCUlNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21rd1ZtTmZRelF5UjBVM05FZzNRVmxOYmpCUlNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c349e8db7e21:0xc37b1cf5e9df7b60"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJIX7b6EnDwoARYHvf6fUce8M/photos/AWCwydheevBhJPOgoNdddNuhthnj-05OLqcvCtvTNsupKGVXlgO6Hksml5CBTtDJkJAamDivVkcd8bFUuMIVf5H_2DI9MOztshzStdCxnVRx8UUyLWFQIPNwUp0D91R8DocZx1Qt5jfzIenrDX5guA_GSWf7mAgPOLRLJOaIgQ0CymtDNcHSWodChd93Gh827iSJze1i71FZPfGGaUWjry7XANqfKIbXtfG8J8SDhqh1ngtNb4tG-60r30k7TpGeBT2F6r23a7_FcynSonuXXPSBNmN3w-_bTGgi0UTaavEWktWjnxmcUCnJtV-4xrp380L7jlnKMQkNwu08DdOvlS9bOoNzdwa3I_ShyhMu4u37nHLMfVo6ED0rBuTWX6DVtryRKkWpLJdGNZt2Tr8hP9jAFu0CXtIwt0X9iAzjtLqTjE9S5WU", "widthPx": 3428, "heightPx": 4800, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "mandarin coffee stand", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/115058914274337501080", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXN7FDqrWcZLkUP8beFEQmV4sKvFwL2RJ2mkTHx4XyEfPDY8PU=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDH4beL_AE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDH4beL_AE!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x